the provinces of Colombia, showing Santander in the centre of the
country can be accessed at:
<http://www.mapsofworld.com/colombia/colombia-political-map.html>. The
HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of South America is available at:
<http://healthmap.org/r/04xQ>. - Mod.CP]
